title: McCarthy drops out of race: Social media reacts
text:
Previous Next 
Bakersfield Congressman and majority leader, Kevin McCarthy announced on Thursday, October 8th that he would drop out of the speaker of the House Race. The news shocked everyone. People around Kern County and beyond shared their thoughts when they heard the announcement.
